773,"uid":191260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"323574231df96f2c071f3263b30a1ebe5c0f7315","tid":2125773,"uid":245775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cb62055c015ce873cd4198f420b8ee9c3a2ba1f","tid":2125773,"uid":183049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0afb8097bfe2863e3fb024efd107527a79f50308","tid":2125773,"uid":191260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"事緣係琴日以抄襲出晒名嘅spoon chan分享咗喺hkblanclub到漂牙，<br />\n跟住比我同巴絲搵到原來呢間係無牌黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaAZ0MK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaAZ0MK.png&h=8e282bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環地址：中環域多利皇后街15至16號裕成商業大廈1樓03室<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">無牌經營黑店 比人拉過一次都仲繼續做生意</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170320/bkn-20170320203754407-0320_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170320%2Fbkn-20170320203754407-0320_00822_001.html&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=092a65bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170320/bkn-20170320203754407-0320_00822_001.html</a><br />\n比人拉段片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncredits to <a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=4d8a6ec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n黃店list上面有佢 有罷工有捐錢<br />\n但又疑似sponsor tvb啲人？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8N0Lc2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8N0Lc2W.png&h=5a486b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vDtaPC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vDtaPC.png&h=9210fc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHi5dis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHi5dis.jpg&h=16232302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzxJKp8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzxJKp8.jpg&h=dcacef7a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72Z8a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72Z8a48.jpg&h=a3b5aca4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hF8ptRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhF8ptRP.jpg&h=ed75c66c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n香港小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被洗版之後佢post咗呢兩個story<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQsEZmm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQsEZmm.png&h=b53c6085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzJwQs2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzJwQs2.png&h=89ca3c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">你個story話好難揀客嚟收錢<br />\n咁係咪姐係咩客都接？黑警都接？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">已經唔關藍定黃事 佢係一間無牌嘅黑店<br />\n整衰咗啲牙真係一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要聲稱黃店 分分鐘呃晒啲同路人去<br />\n整衰晒佢地啲牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>香港牙醫學會會長廖偉明表示，近年收到不少個案，涉及市民到美容院漂牙後，需由牙醫「執手尾」，出現牙肉發炎及萎縮，更有因牙齒極度敏感或痛楚需要杜牙根。他又指，無牌牙醫診所如未有徹底消毒，愛滋病和乙型肝炎等更有機會經殘留在醫療工具上的唾液或血液傳播。<br />\ncredits to <a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=4d8a6ec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a></blockquote></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ArcJJVr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FArcJJVr.png&h=23b3a565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話自己係正當beauty同有註冊<br />\n咁就要問下衛生署先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電話:2836 0077<br />\n傳真:2836 0072<br />\ne-mail:crd@dh.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n承諾回覆時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初步回覆:收到投訴後十天內<br />\n詳細回覆:收到投訴後三十天內<br />\n記得留意email呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家繼續補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"Diu 之前去hkbalance飄過一次牙<br />\nIG寫$500幾一次 好 我就去左整<br />\n點知整完牙只係白左2度都算 <br />\n去到比錢嗰陣 條友係咁叫我join plan <br />\n我話唔join 之後條友叫我比千幾蚊埋單<br />\n我即刻show ig張相出黎 話 下你張相寫係$500幾<br />\n佢話join plan先500幾一次 唔join就千幾蚊<br />\n屌 咁你IG就咪撚寫$500幾一次啦 𠱓神騙鬼<br />\n正一黑店"},{"pid":"d7d37617e5154c6f31a14ff9cd836467be498599","tid":2125773,"uid":183049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0afb8097bfe2863e3fb024efd107527a79f50308","tid":2125773,"uid":191260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"事緣係琴日以抄襲出晒名嘅spoon chan分享咗喺hkblanclub到漂牙，<br />\n跟住比我同巴絲搵到原來呢間係無牌黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaAZ0MK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaAZ0MK.png&h=8e282bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環地址：中環域多利皇后街15至16號裕成商業大廈1樓03室<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">無牌經營黑店 比人拉過一次都仲繼續做生意</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170320/bkn-20170320203754407-0320_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170320%2Fbkn-20170320203754407-0320_00822_001.html&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=092a65bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170320/bkn-20170320203754407-0320_0